<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>net5.0-windows</TargetFramework>
    <UseWPF>true</UseWPF>
	<GenerateDocumentationFile>true</GenerateDocumentationFile>
    <Authors>Salvatore Peluso</Authors>
    <Description>This package includes a reworked, fully customizable, version of the most commonly used controls, plus some new special controls and extra functionality.

A fully description, and examples, can be found on github here: https://github.com/devpelux/fullcontrols

The complete documentation can be found here: https://github.com/devpelux/fullcontrols/wiki</Description>
    <PackageLicenseExpression></PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageTags>xaml library control csharp nuget-packages dark-theme wpf accordion button menu window context-menu collapsible wpf-controls flat-design wpf-ui passwordbox net-5</PackageTags>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>Added Collapsible decorator.
Added Accordion control.
Added AccordionItem control.
Added SimpleAccordionItem control.
Added ItemsControlAccordionItem control.
Removed ActionEventArgs and all action events from EWindow.
Added BeforeClosing and BeforeMinimizing cancelable events to EWindow.
Added more properties to better customize EWindow caption buttons, toolbar, and behaviour.
Added FlatContextMenu and FlatMenu.
Removed PolymorphicMenuItem and replaced with FlatMenuItem, FlatMenuSeparator, FlatMenuSpace and FlatMenuTitle.
Added radio-checking (mutually exclusive checking) feature to FlatMenuItem.
Added more properties for menu items customization.
Updated many controls to use FlatContextMenu.
Updated GlassScrollViewer and GlassScrollBar to be more consistent and added more properties to customize them.
Updated many controls to use GlassScrollViewer.
General optimizations and bugfixes.</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/devpelux/fullcontrols</PackageProjectUrl>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/devpelux/fullcontrols</RepositoryUrl>
    <Copyright>Copyright (c) 2020-2021 devpelux (Salvatore Peluso)</Copyright>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <PackageIcon>FullControls.png</PackageIcon>
    <Version>1.3.0</Version>
    <PackageLicenseFile>LICENSE</PackageLicenseFile>
